{"tid":890760,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食評]—蛇王二","createTime":"2018-11-05T14:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T17:53:10.000Z","uid":182683,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8c5387afb9b7269b9be42c91010e0f6493026d","tid":890760,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"依排好勤力！！狂出po爽呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次黎到依間位於銅鑼灣地鋪，啲伙記好串嘅蛇王二！我得閒就會食下，不過唔係食蛇，係食燒味同膶腸！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鴨脾肥叉飯$67<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8aW72cj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8aW72cj.png&h=62b85b94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n味道：食得鴨緊係食啲肉羶味，唔係我誇張，依到啲鴨味係特別勁，好重肉個種甜味。我自己比較鍾意肥嘅燒味，但鴨本身瘦，所以叫左脾就岩岩好。同埋依到個鴨皮好薄，正！<br />\n<br />\n到肥叉啦，燒得夠燶，個邊有少少黑色仲脆脆地先會香口好食，正！而且啲叉燒應該係啲靚少少嘅梅頭黎，三邊肉中間都有有少少筋同有塊肥膏係中間，岩岩好肉同肥膏各半，啲油香正到！！！<br />\n肉質咬落都夠琳，不過我個人鍾意有少少咬口同埋切厚少少個種。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：係貴左少少，份量一定夠飽，叫蹀貴$5蚊先多少少飯唔知點解，不過啲野食真係正，銅鑼灣食算係咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cisryju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcisryju.png&h=83c24428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n膶腸$16<br />\n<br />\n味道：我唔記得影相，次次都會叫一條食，好重個啲內臟嘅甜味(唔知大家明唔明），舊舊都好似食緊濃縮左幾倍嘅豬膶咁好甜，詳細我唔知入面落左啲咩，總之好正！！！<br />\n<br />\n價錢：正常價，但咁好味抵啦！<br />\n<br />\n個白飯就正常，不得不提杯奶茶幾好飲，個茶底整得幾好，好香！！<br />\n啲伙記成日好嬲咁黑曬面，你食多幾次會發現佢地剩係會對住大陸人先係咁！爽！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27HGndc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27HGndc.png&h=414859f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91xWa6z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91xWa6z.png&h=da11577b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n評語：燒到冚冚聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n評分：7/10<br />\n溝女指數：3/10<br />\n囡囡：唔好坐同埋有蛇，又打唔到卡，乞衣先食燒味飯。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=%2BAsIOPlVLiug4t6yw5b%2BDr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a77a9b7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a>"},{"pid":"80fef247ddc8ce737e5811c6bed0c1189b0c32a6","tid":890760,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>乞衣先食燒味飯</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來我都做咗好多年乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20335f5911a8023525742d1bc859fbfd601b59ee","tid":890760,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6fc1a3fef0191c9198690c1fa394b5d97f8177","tid":890760,"uid":105614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似ok"},{"pid":"42a6d610030588c47008d66d057df75f179dd6c5","tid":890760,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"我ig有食野片睇可以清楚啲！<br />\n因為啲伙記係咁望住我，今次啲相影得唔好對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf633c40899f3f49bb8120148396ca77cdb61f15","tid":8